parameters: \n<???>Ha...\.\.\.  has someone finally come to attend to me...\.\.\. ?\.\.

Sprawled out on the couch is a blonde girl.\.\. Her hair is done up in a ponytail and her long pointed ears are noticeable,\. marking her as not entirely human.\.\.  She wears a short red dress and dark stockings.\.\.
She looks halfway between asleep and spaced out,\. not really looking at you as her eyes flutter,\. hand lazily dangling over the couch edge.\.\.
\n<???>Ha...\.\.\.  has someone finally come to attend to me...\.\.\. ?\.\.
She yawns,\. voice squeaking slightly as she turns.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>The hell are you calling a maid?\.\. Do I look like I'm here to "attend" you?\.\.
Neneko scoffs,\. twitching her tail.\.\. The woman doesn't respond,\. however,\. her eyes drifting closed as her breathing slows.\.\.
This scene will be ready in one of the next builds!\.\. Thank you for playing up to this point!
Neneko roughly pushes the woman's shoulder,\. causing her to grumble and weakly wave her hand in protest.\.\.
\n<???>Ugh...\.\.\.  so harsh...\.\.\.  were you raised in a cave...\.\.\. ?\.\. Mnnf...\.\.\. The head maid will hear of this...\.\.\. not that she'd do anything,\. bitch...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Talk about living the high life.\.\. Wake up "ma'am",\. you have a guest with a whole lot of formal complaints.\.\.
Neneko shakes her again,\. the woman groaning and whining.\.\.
\n<???>Ohh...\.\.\. fine,\. fine,\. just get me my drink,\. you know I can't work or show myself like this...\.\.\.
\n<???>And enough with the shaking...\.\.\. yawn...\.\.\. I feel like my brain's going to roll out of my eyes...\.\.\. And that will be very unsightly,\. I assure you...\.\.\. zzz...\.\.\.
Neneko growls,\. impatiently rubbing her forehead in frustration.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Honestly,\. rich people.\.\. You want your drink,\. fine,\. I'll get your damn drink.\.\. Where is it?\.\.
The woman grumbles,\. weakly raising a hand and pointing at a table at the corner of the room,\. a red bottle and wine glass set atop it.\.\.
Ignoring the blondie's quiet complaints about the help having no respect,\. Neneko steps away.\.\.
Neneko crouches,\. staring into the woman's eyes.\.\. She looks completely out of it,\. not really looking at her as her eyes flutter sleepily.\.\.
The cat sighs,\. scratching her head,\. before...\.\.\.
The woman winces,\. turning away and covering her ears.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Seriously,\. get up before I flip this couch over!\.\. You're not allowed to look this dead until I find out whether or not I should be killing you!\.\.
\n<???>Oh lovely,\. did she send you here to torture me?\.\. What an awful sound,\. like scratched glass on my poor ears.\.\. Really,\. what's with the noise...\.\.\. ?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Wh-\.what did you say about my voice,\. bitch!?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Whatever.\.\. Honestly,\. it's the middle of the day,\. get up.\.\.
\n<???>Even if you say that,\. it's not like I can...\.\.\.
\n<???>Enough mockery.\.\. Get me my drink,\. will you?\.\. Even that poor quality mix you've been feeding me is better than nothing...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>You always wake up to a glass of wine?\.\. Classy.\.\.
\n<???>Har har.\.\. I'm paying you maids too much...\.\.\. enough with the talking,\. more with the feeding...\.\.\.
She lazily motions over to a table in the corner,\. a bottle and glass sitting atop it.\.\. Neneko rolls her eyes.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Hah...\.\.\. well,\. not the first whiny brat I've had to get out of bed.\.\.
Neneko rolls her shoulders.\.\. It was time for all her training as a big sister to come into play.\.\.
She eyes the woman,\. snoozing blissfully unaware of her terrible fate...\.\.\.
\n<???>Ack!\.\. Wha-\.ah!\.\. Ahaha!\.\. N-\.no,\. what are you doing!\.\.
Neneko furiously begins to tickle the girl,\. pinning her down with her legs.\.\. The blonde woman squirms and whines between giggles.\.\.
\n<???>Y-\.you animal!\.\. You are the worst maid ever!\.\.
Stop touching me,\. I'm a pure girl!\.\.
\n<???>Get off!\.\. Unhand me!\.\. What sort of treatment is this!?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>The kinda treatment you get when you're a bad girl that oversleeps.\.\. Now up and at 'em before I get the ice bucket.\.\.
\n<???>Y-\.you...\.\.\. !!\.\. You are a monster!\.\. Enough of this!\.\.
She hugs herself,\. whimpering as she cowers from your assault,\. defeated.\.\.
\n<???>M-\.my wine,\. I can't wake up without my wine,\. go grab it already!\.\.
\n<???>Y-\.yes,\. yes,\. just get off of me...\.\.\.
Neneko hops off of the couch,\. dusting off her paws.\.\. The lady just buries her face in the cushion,\. dead to the world.\.\.
\n<???>Guhhh...\.\.\. Why are all my maids so exhausting to deal with...\.\.\. !?\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Jeez.\.\. What kinda fancy room is this?\.\. Someone's dramatic...\.\.\.
